property.name: note
property.value:
param progress: 0 - null 1 - beginning 2 - button 1 3 - button 2 4 - button 3
Upon pressing each button, we increment "progress" up 1. The quantized transition regions then send the playhead forward on the next barline. Volume automation on each track dictates which track we're hearing, and how the different moments in progression crossfade.
Also, we're using the same "escape" parameter and effect as in event:/music/lvl2/chase. See that event for more info.
